<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body       { font-family: sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 24px; }
      h1         { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #1a1a2e; }
      .summary   { background: #f4f6ff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 24px 0; }
      .btn       { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #4a6cf7; color: #fff;
                   text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin: 24px 0; }
      .footer    { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 16px; }
      a          { color: #4a6cf7; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>👋 Good morning, <%= @user.name %>!</h1>

    <div class="summary">
      Your <strong>daily open tickets report</strong> for
      <strong><%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong> is ready.
    </div>

    <p>The attached CSV contains all currently open tickets with customer and agent details.</p>

    <%= link_to "⬇ Download Report", @url, class: "btn" %>

    <div class="footer">
      You're receiving this as a member of the support team.<br />
    </div>
  </body>
</html>